features: High-Quality Paper Napkins - Made from premium quality paper, these 2-ply napkins are durable and strong enough to clean up spills and messes with ease. They are also soft to the touch, making them gentle on the skin.

Large Size Cocktail Napkins - With an unfolded size of 13 x 13 inches, these napkins are large enough to handle any spills and messes, suitable for use as a luncheon napkin or for any meal. Their ample size also makes them perfect for creative table settings.

Convenient Pack Size and Disposable - This 40 pack of napkins ensures you have a sufficient quantity for weddings, engagements, or romantic evenings. The convenience of disposability means quick and easy cleanup, letting you enjoy your special moments without the hassle.

Adorable Heart Pattern Design - Decorated with a cute heart pattern, these napkins add a touch of love to your table decor. The playful and romantic design is perfect for Valentine's Day or celebrating love and commitment on special occasions.

Perfect for Valentine's Day and Romantic Decorations - These napkins are not just functional; they're also an essential part of your decoration, enhancing the romance and special atmosphere of your event, be it a Valentine's Day dinner, an engagement party, or just a special night in.
